vimeo_data.name: A Photographer's True North
vimeo_data.description:
At Colby, Edwin Torres '12 found his true north and followed it ever since. A renowned photojournalist who helped earn a Pulitzer Prize with ProPublica, Torres today documents his home neighborhood of the Bronx and works for the mayor's office in New York.

Direction/Production: Milton Guillén 
Cinematography/Art: Nicolas Abaunza
Line production: Sara Verstynen, Mareisa Weil 
Consultant producer: Phil Newsom
Post-production producer: Jon Applebaum
Edition: Neighborhood Film Co/Daniel Gauthier
Sound design: Bobb Barito
Original score: Makeup and Vanity Set / Matthew Pusti
Graphic Design: Kirsten Marjerison
Executive producers: Anthony Ronzio, Ruth Jackson, Gerry Boyle.
